                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-560" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN HARRISON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 32.) I was called to Mr. Best's on Thursday last, about two o'clock—I went into the parlour—the prisoner was sitting down, and this bag, containing eight pots, was on the table—one of them is Mr. Best's.</p>
               <p>
